  <section class="section">
    <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container medium w-container">
      <div class="heading-images">
        <h1 class="heading-cta text-weight-regular">
          <strong>Building Digital Growth with Strategy and Creativity</strong>
        </h1>
        <div class="text-wrapper">
          <div class="intro-text">
            What started with <strong>curiosity</strong> has turned into a <strong
            >
            </strong>journey <div class="span one"></div> through digital commerce
            and strategy, product development, and customer experience management.
            With in-depth experience and a portfolio of successful projects, I blend
            <strong>creativity</strong>
            <div class="span two"></div> with <strong>technology</strong>
            <div class="span three"></div> to help brands connect, engage, and grow.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container w-container">
      <div
        data-w-id="dc6a7daf-0a7b-ccdc-43d3-d22391b2e2ca"
        style="opacity:0"
        class="cards-grid"
      >
