                leaders. Shaped companies in fostering growth, strengthening
                operations, and creating sustainable structures while preserving
                agility. Developed strategies and processes that strengthened
                their competitive position in local and global markets.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          id="w-node-dc6a7daf-0a7b-ccdc-43d3-d22391b2e2d5-f1ee5fbb"
          class="grid-card"
