            <div class="card-big-number">+32</div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid-content">
            <div class="text-weight-medium text-size-large">
              Markets activated
            </div>
            <div class="opacity-88">
              <div class="card-text">
                Activated and enhanced markets across diverse contexts - shaping
                localized e-commerce strategies, orchestrating global
                marketplace launches, and facilitating large-scale digital
                product rollouts of loyalty and personalization features for
                millions of customers.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
